text: Chetyrbash () is a rural locality (a village) in Miyakinsky Selsoviet, Miyakinsky District, Bashkortostan, Russia. The population was 117 as of 2010. There are 2 streets. == Geography == It is located 6 km from Kirgiz-Miyaki. == References == Category:Rural localities in Miyakinsky District
title: Chetyrbash
